{"amendement": {"@xmlns": "http://schemas.assemblee-nationale.fr/referentiel", "uid": "AMANR5L17PO59048B0324P2D1N000058", "chronotag": "1739874545733", "legislature": "17", "identification": {"numeroLong": "II-CF58", "numeroOrdreDepot": "58", "prefixeOrganeExamen": "CION_FIN", "numeroRect": "0"}, "examenRef": "EXANR5L17PO59048B0324P2D1", "texteLegislatifRef": "PRJLANR5L17B0324", "triAmendement": "beoaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaasahx", "cardinaliteAmdtMultiples": "1", "amendementParentRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "signataires": {"auteur": {"typeAuteur": "D\u00e9put\u00e9", "gouvernementRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "acteurRef": "PA720976", "groupePolitiqueRef": "PO845485", "auteurRapporteurOrganeRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "cosignataires": {"acteurRef": ["PA267763", "PA719138", "PA719286", "PA795244", "PA721110", "PA720960", "PA796078"]}, "suffixe": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "libelle": "M.&#160;Mathiasin,  M.&#160;Bataille, M.&#160;Castellani, M.&#160;Colombani, M.&#160;Lenormand, Mme&#160;Sanquer, M.&#160;Serva et Mme&#160;Youssouffa"}, "pointeurFragmentTexte": {"partieAmendableRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "division": {"titre": "\u00c9TAT B", "articleDesignationCourte": "ART. 42", "articleDesignation": "ARTICLE 42", "type": "ANNEXE", "avant_A_Apres": "A", "divisionRattachee": "ARTICLE 42", "articleAdditionnel": "false", "chapitreAdditionnel": "false", "urlDivisionTexteVise": "/17/textes/0324C.asp#D_Etat_B"}, "missionVisee": {"codeEtat": "B", "codeMissionMinefi": "OA", "libelleMission": "Outre-mer", "missionRef": "2880"}}, "corps": {"cartoucheInformatif": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenuAuteur": {"dispositifAmdtCreditPLF": {"listeProgrammes": {"programme": [{"libelle": "Emploi outre-mer", "programmeRef": "367112", "autorisationEngagement": "-2000000", "creditPaiement": "-2000000", "action": "modification", "lignesCredits": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, {"libelle": "Conditions de vie outre-mer", "programmeRef": "367114", "autorisationEngagement": "2000000", "creditPaiement": "2000000", "action": "modification", "lignesCredits": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}]}, "soldeAE": "0", "soldeCP": "0", "cpEgalAe": "true"}, "avantAppel": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "exposeSommaire": "<p>Cet amendement vise &#x00E0; augmenter de 2 millions d&#x2019;euros le fonds de continuit&#x00E9; territoriale afin de mieux accompagner la mobilit&#x00E9; des Ultramarins en cette p&#x00E9;riode de forte inflation et d&#x2019;augmentation insoutenable du prix des billets d&#x2019;avion.</p><p>En effet, dans le budget de la mission Outre-mer pour 2025, les cr&#x00E9;dits consacr&#x00E9;s &#x00E0; la continuit&#x00E9; territoriale baissent significativement&nbsp;: -17,6 M&#x20AC;.</p><p>Or, la continuit&#x00E9; territoriale est un enjeu crucial de justice r&#x00E9;publicaine, d&#x2019;&#x00E9;galit&#x00E9;.</p><p>Aussi est-il propos&#x00E9; les mouvements de cr&#x00E9;dits suivants&nbsp;:</p><p>- Une augmentation de 2&nbsp;000 000&nbsp;euros des cr&#x00E9;dits de l&#x2019;action 03 &#x00AB;&nbsp;Continuit&#x00E9; territoriale&nbsp;&#x00BB; du programme 123 &#x00AB;&nbsp;Conditions de vie Outre-mer&nbsp;&#x00BB;&nbsp;;</p><p>- Une diminution de 2&nbsp;000 000&nbsp;euros des cr&#x00E9;dits de l&#x2019;action 01 &#x00AB;&nbsp;Soutien aux entreprises&nbsp;&#x00BB; du programme 138 &#x00AB;&nbsp;Emploi Outre-mer&nbsp;&#x00BB;.</p><p>Cette r&#x00E9;duction a pour but de se conformer aux exigences de la loi organique relative aux lois de finances (LOLF) qui oblige, lorsque l&#x2019;auteur d&#x2019;un amendement souhaite augmenter les cr&#x00E9;dits d&#x2019;un programme, &#x00E0; diminuer les cr&#x00E9;dits d&#x2019;un autre programme d&#x2019;autant. Il n&#x2019;est donc en r&#x00E9;alit&#x00E9; pas envisag&#x00E9; de restreindre les moyens allou&#x00E9;s aux entreprises d&#x2019;Outre-mer mais bien d'attribuer de nouveaux moyens au fonds de continuit&#x00E9; territoriale.</p><p>En cons&#x00E9;quence, les signataires du pr&#x00E9;sent amendement demandent au Gouvernement de lever le gage.</p>", "annexeExposeSommaire": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "cycleDeVie": {"dateDepot": "2024-10-16", "datePublication": "2024-11-15", "soumisArticle40": "true", "etatDesTraitements": {"etat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Discut\u00e9"}, "sousEtat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Retir\u00e9"}}, "dateSort": "2024-11-04T09:55:04+01:00", "sort": "Retir\u00e9"}, "representations": {"representation": {"nom": "PDF", "typeMime": {"type": "application", "subType": "PDF"}, "statutRepresentation": {"verbatim": "true", "canonique": "true", "officielle": "true", "transcription": "false", "enregistrement": "false"}, "repSource": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "offset": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenu": {"documentURI": "/base/AMANR5L17PO59048B0324P2D1N000058?format=pdf"}, "dateDispoRepresentation": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "seanceDiscussionRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "article99": "false", "loiReference": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "discussionCommune": {"idDiscussion": "27718", "typePosition": "Milieu"}, "discussionIdentique": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "accordGouvernement